'''Diiwal Benue''' ɗun diiwal ɗer hautugo [[Naajeeriya]]. E gal wodii mangu lesdi kamani kilomita 34,059km e ɗuɗuki yimɓe 4,253,641 e limgal ɗuɗirka yimɓe gal ɗungu 2006.Gelle mauɗe diiwal gal honje gonii makurɗi Samuel Ortom hanko wonii Arɗiɗi diiwal gal tun e subtugo dungu gu 2015 ha waddi hanɗe. Ballowo arɗiɗo hanko wonii Beson Abounu.
Sanata en diiwal gal hanɓe goni David Mark, George Akume e Barnabas Andyar Gemade.

1.	Fiyoɓe bauɗi denno ɓe Benue

2.	Jangoɓe ɓe benue

Diiwal Benue gal hauti kerol e diiwe hajewe go o kanje gonii; Cross Rivers, Ebonyi, Enugu, Kogi, Nasarawa, ɗen e Taraba.

